OpenCL
.
├── clean.sh
├── OpenCL-Wrapper
├── OpenCL-Wrapper.x
├── README
└── submit.OpenCL.slurm



OpenCL-Wrapper: directory with all sources 
(for an updated version clone from https://github.com/ProjectPhysX/OpenCL-Wrapper)

OpenCL-Wrapper.x: precompiled exe

* to clean directory
	./clean.sh

* to compile fortran code:
	./compile.fortran.sh

* to submit a job
	sbatch submit.OpenCL.slurm

